#

Classic Irish Soda Bread

55 min
$2.5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

Irish

Course:

Bread

Tags:

BreadQuickComfort Food

Description

A simple, fluffy bread made with buttermilk and baking soda, perfect for slathering with butter or enjoying with soups.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 4 cups
  • baking soda: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • buttermilk: 1.5 cups
  • butter (optional): 2 tablespoons
